      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "About 09:45 he was returning from the Post Exchange when he called",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "to me to come outside and asked me to look up to where he was pointing",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "and to my surprise I saw two (2) flying objects which appeared to me like",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "two (2) flying disc or saucer shaped silver colored objects, flying in a",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "northwestern direction at speed approximately 350 or 400 miles per hour",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "and at an altitude of about 7500 or 8000 feet. I could not hear a motor",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "roar like one of our planes and it could not have been a balloon.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "I am of good health and sound mind and this was no hallucination.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
